<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http_equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="font-family: 'Oxygen', sans-serif"> Please Remember Confirmation Email </h2>
    <p style="font-family: 'Oxygen', sans-serif; font-size: 14px">
      Hi there! You or someone with your email address (<%= @user.email %>) signed up to receive a joyful reminder
      from me once daily. Click the link below to verify:<br>
    </p>
    <a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="<%= @verify_url %>" target="_blank" style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Oxygen, sans-serif; font-weight: bold">Verify</a>
    <p style="font-family: 'Oxygen', sans-serif; font-size: 14px">
      If you don't click the link, I won't send you any more emails. Either way, know someone was thinking about you and thought you'd like this!<br>
      Thanks and I love you
    </p>
    <br>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Oxygen', sans-serif;">Click here to <a href="<%= @unsubscribe_url %>">unsubscribe</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
